## ğŸ”§ Installation

## 1. **Install Ollama**

### On **Linux**:

```bash
curl -fsSL https://ollama.com/install.sh | sh
```

### On **Windows** or **macOS**:

Download the installer from:  
[https://ollama.com/download](https://ollama.com/download)

